      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. my main concern is that if it gets too dense, it might feel too stiff or \"closed off\" for the luxury market. we really need that tight, uniform structure to prevent any fraying or loose threads during the finishing process. how much of an increase in pick count would you suggest to ensure the integrity of the weave without making it feel like a heavy canvas?",
